posts.description: Yay or nay? 🙆🙌 Grilled flat iron steak with chimichurri... 😘😗 Last week, Mixt opened its ninth location at Yerba Buena Lane. Exclusively to this location, you'll see a whole new menu option called "market plates". If you like fish, you must also try their grilled columbia river steelhead with miso ginger glaze. 🤗 #Steak

One whole peking duck, please! 😍 We thoroughly enjoyed slices of @ChinaLiveSF's crispy melt-in-your-mouth peking duck and would gladly go back for more. 😋😗 In addition, we had their xiao long bao, pan-fried pork dumplings, pork & chive dumplings, pork belly lotus buns and salt & pepper dungeness crab. See more on the blog (link in profile). Where is your favorite shop for peking duck? 🤔 My other favorite would have to be Great China in Berkeley.

Can you tell what I'm having? 🍝🤔 It's large meatballs and meat ravioli topped with bolognese sauce! 🙆🙌 I love drizzling balsamic over my meatballs. Am I the only one who does this...? 😋🙂 Seriously, where else can you have tasty meatballs and fresh pasta???

Yas yas yasss!!! 🙆🙌 #Jajangmyeon: a Korean Chinese noodle dish topped with a thick sauce made of black bean, diced pork and vegetables and sometimes seafood. 😋🙂 This tasted extremely yummy! I don't remember the last time I had jajangmyeon. My belly is SO happy right now! 😗❤ Where is your favorite jajangmyeon? 🤔

When in San Jose, you can easily find many broken rice plate places. 🙆🙌 My order: special rice combo with BBQ pork, fried shrimp cake, shredded pork skins, egg cake, BBQ shrimp and grilled shrimp on sugarcane. 😋😗
Where is your favorite broken rice plate...? 🤔
❥ Com Tam Dat Thanh
❥ Com Tam Thien Huong

Newly opened ramen shop serves Hakata-style ramen with rich pork broth, braised pork belly, soft boiled egg, corn, green onions, kikurage mushroom and bean sprouts! 🍲🤗 This shop also specializes in chicken paitan ramen but I decided to try their Hakata tonkotsu ramen first. Has anyone tried Marufuku? Thoughts? 🤔
